= Felicjan Lechnicki

Felicjan Lechnicki is a staunch advocate of strengthening the government and improving the economic position of rural Poland. He focuses on constitutional reforms that centralize executive power, enhance economic opportunities for workers and farmers, and unite the rural movement to increase its political influence.

