@constitutional_reforms
title: Constitutional Reforms for a Strong Executive
subtitle: Push for reforms that strengthen the executive branch and establish a stable, democratic government.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 8
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before the next action. ?]
#go-to: reform_plan.executive_reforms_implemented

Felicjan Lechnicki advocates for constitutional reforms to centralize power in the executive branch, ensuring a stable, strong, and democratic government. These changes secure the government’s long-term ability to implement effective policies but could face opposition from parliamentary supporters.

@economic_improvements
title: Economic Improvements for Workers and Farmers
subtitle: Improve the economic conditions of agriculture, industry, and trade while protecting social and economic gains.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 8
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before the next action. ?]
#go-to: reform_plan.economic_reforms_implemented

Lechnicki supports policies that improve the economic situation for farmers, workers, and small businesses. These reforms aim to maintain social and economic achievements while balancing the interests of both agriculture and industry.

@unite_rural_movement
title: Unify the Rural Movement
subtitle: Bring together the rural political movements to strengthen their influence in the government.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before the next action. ?]
#go-to: unity_plan.rural_unity_achieved

Felicjan seeks to unite rural political factions to ensure their agenda is aligned with national interests. By creating a unified front, the rural movement can increase its influence in shaping government policies, though this may lead to friction with urban political interests.